---
import Section from '../layout/Section.astro';
import CTAButton from '../ui/CTAButton.astro';
---

<Section id="orbesg" class="flex flex-col">
  <div id="orbesg-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-50 md:opacity-100 md:translate-x-1/4"></div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[1] bg-gradient-to-b from-black/40 via-transparent to-black/60 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-6 md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 text-center">
    <span class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 md:mb-4 block">Featured Project</span>
    <a href="https://criora.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block group">
      <img src="/assets/images/criora-logo.svg" alt="Criora" class="h-10 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
    </a>
    <p class="text-xl text-white/70">
      Climate Risk Intelligence for Any Location
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex-1"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Challenge</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">Climate risk</span> assessments across many sites mean manual spreadsheets, expensive consultants, and environmental data that's hard to fold into <span class="text-white/70">ESG</span> and operational risk frameworks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Solution</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">Score any address</span> on Earth in seconds. Site-level physical climate risk with <a href="https://criora.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">TCFD-aligned reports</a>. Pick a location, run the analysis, review the report.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Technology</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="gradient-text font-medium">Data pipelines</span> fuse ECMWF ERA5 reanalysis, Copernicus drought indicators, IPCC AR6 sea-level projections, and Aqueduct water stress with live feeds from NASA FIRMS, GDACS, and USGS into per-site risk scores.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col justify-end lg:items-end">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 lg:mt-0">
          <CTAButton href="https://criora.com" variant="secondary" external>
            Visit Criora
          </CTAButton>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"/>
            <path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">15 Physical Risks</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            Temperature, precipitation, wind, flood, drought, sea level rise and more, scored for any coordinate worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">TCFD-Aligned Reports</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            Disclosure-ready output mapped to TCFD, CSRD, and EU Taxonomy, with risks, drivers, and recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/>
            <path d="M12 3v3M12 18v3M3 12h3M18 12h3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">Live Event Radar</h4>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            Track active wildfires, floods, cyclones, and heatwaves near any monitored location in real time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full text-center pb-6">
    <p class="text-white/40 text-xs">
      Climate Risk Platform · 2025
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
